response.original_title: Gary Delaney Second Special (Full Show) Comedy Club Classics 2014-2017
response.overview: Gary Delaney's "Second Special (Full Show) Comedy Club Classics 2014-2017" is a comedy extravaganza featuring the best of his hilariously sharp one-liners and witty observations. This special compiles his standout moments from various comedy clubs during the 2014-2017 period.  Delaney's comedic prowess shines as he delivers rapid-fire punchlines and clever wordplay. His humor covers a wide range of subjects, from everyday situations to bizarre scenarios, offering a fresh and relatable take on life's absurdities. Each joke is a gem, leaving the audience in fits of laughter.
response.title: Gary Delaney Second Special (Full Show) Comedy Club Classics 2014-2017
